<div class="container-std custom-content">
    <strong>THE PROJECT</strong>
    <p>I was asked to improve the home screen of the app with the following considerations:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>It should be clear to first time users where they shall start learning, as this is the most important
            component</li>
        <li>Revisiting users shall easy find where they left off</li>
    </ul>

    <strong>MY ROLE</strong>
    <p>I took ownership of the project and created Use Cases, Onboarding and User Journeys, as well as a new layout and
        design of the home screen</p>

    <strong>THE RESULT</strong>
    <p>The outcome led to much improved UX where the new approach covered all the userâ€™s needs. The new layout of the
        home screen created better navigation and users would easier find the content. The client was delighted with the
        new version</p>
</div>

    <div class="py-16 sm:py-20 md:py-28 lg:py-32"></div>






